metadata.description:
The progress bar widget  show how many humans have been proved with I-AM-HUMAN soul-bound-token out of 1000 humans.
Colors are taken from NDC Brand assets. Colors used in widget are : #F29BC0 and #FFD50D

Props for component: widgetBarWidth: number
When use component widgetBarWidth will set max width of element. 
Max width is limited on mobile & small tablets. 
So use widgetBarWidth for desktop max width. Default is 300px
